kas]]\n|[[William T. Young]]\n|1:17.74\n|-\n|1990\n|[[Deposit Ticket]]\n|[[Gary Stevens (jockey)|Gary Stevens]]\n|[[D. Wayne Lukas]]\n|[[Overbrook Farm]]\n|1:16.20\n|-\n|1989\n|[[Summer Squall]]\n|[[Pat Day]]\n|[[Neil J. Howard]]\n|[[Dogwood Stable]]\n|1:16.80\n|-\n|1988\n|[[Mercedes Won]]\n|[[Robbie Davis]]\n|[[Arnold Fink]]\n|Christopher Spencer\n|1:16.60\n|-\n|1987\n|[[Crusader Sword]]\n|[[Randy Romero]]\n|[[MacKenzie Miller]]\n|[[Rokeby Stable]]\n|1:18.60\n|-\n|1986\n|[[Gulch (horse)|Gulch]]\n|[[Angel Cordero Jr.]]\n|[[Leroy Jolley]]\n|[[Peter M. Brant]]\n|1:16.40\n|-\n|1985\n|[[Papal Power]]\n|[[Don MacBeth]]\n|[[Charles Peoples]]\n|[[Bayard Sharp]]\n|1:18.40\n|-\n|1984\n|[[Chief's Crown]]\n|[[Don MacBeth]]\n|[[Roger Laurin]]\n|Star Crown Stable\n|1:16.00\n|-\n|1983\n|[[Capitol South (horse)|Capitol South]]\n|[[Jerry D. Bailey]]\n|[[Lou Rondinello]]\n|[[Darby Dan Farm]]\n|1:17.40\n|-\n|1982\n|[[Copelan]]\n|[[Jerry D. Bailey]]\n|[[Mitchell Griffin]]\n|[[Fred W. Hooper]]\n|1:16.60\n|-\n|1981\n|[[Timely Writer]]\n|[[Roger Danjean]]\n|[[Dominic Imprescia]]\n|Peter Martin\n|1:16.20\n|-\n|1980\n|[[Tap Shoes]]\n|[[Ruben Hernandez (jockey)|Ruben Hernandez]]\n|[[Howard M. Tesher]]\n|[[Leone J. Peters]]\n|1:17.00\n|-\n|1979*\n|[[J.P. Brother]]\n|[[Joseph Imparato]]\n|[[John P. Campo]]\n|Diamond Peg Stable\n|1:16.20\n|-\n|1978\n|[[General Assembly (horse)|General Assembly]]\n|[[Darrel McHargue]]\n|[[Leroy Jolley]]\n|[[Bertram R. Firestone]]\n|1:16.40\n|-\n|1977\n|[[Affirmed]]\n|[[Steve Cauthen]]\n|[[Laz Barrera]]\n|[[Harbor View Farm]]\n|1:15.40\n|-\n|1976\n|[[Banquet Table]]\n|[[Jean Cruguet]]\n|[[George T. Poole Jr.]]\n|[[Cornelius Vanderbilt Whitney|C. V. Whitney]]\n|1:16.20\n|-\n|1975-I\n|[[Jackknife (horse)|Jackknife]]\n|[[Jean Cruguet]]\n|[[John P. Campo]]\n|[[Elmendorf Farm]]\n|1:16.60\n|-\n|1975-II\n|[[Eustace (horse)|Eustace]]\n|[[James D. Nichols|James Nichols]]\n|[[Wayne Rose]]\n|Eugene Cashman\n|1:16.40\n|-\n|1974-I\n|[[The Bagel Prince]]\n|[[Angel Cordero Jr.